column2:

column1:

 lldp global enable
#
 undo dot1x access-user log enable abnormal-logoff failed-login normal-logoff successful-login

#
 undo port-security mac-move permit
 port-security access-user log enable failed-authorization mac-learning violation

column2:

#

column1:
mac-address mac-move fast-update
#
 loopback-detection global enable vlan 1 to 4094 
 loopback-detection interval-time 5
#
column2:
mac-address mac-move fast-update
#
 lldp global enable
#
 loopback-detection global enable vlan 1 to 4094
 loopback-detection interval-time 5
#

#
line class aux
 authentication-mode password
 user-role network-admin
#

column1:
undo user-role network-operator
#
 arp mac-interface-consistency check enable
#

#
 info-center loghost 192.168.30.251
 info-center loghost source Vlan-interface400
 info-center source SYSLOG loghost level warning
#
column2:
#
 info-center loghost source Vlan-interface400
 info-center loghost 192.168.30.251
 info-center source SYSLOG loghost level warning
#

#
 undo http-redirect https-port
#
 security-enhanced level 1
#
return

column1:
user-group system
#
undo password-control complexity user-name check
column2:
user-group system
 undo password-control complexity user-name check

column1:
#
 snmp-agent
 snmp-agent trap enable
 snmp-agent community write simple U-NET
 snmp-agent sys-info version v2c 
 snmp-agent target-host trap address udp-domain 192.168.30.251 params securityname U-NET v2c
 snmp-agent trap source vlan-interface 400
 snmp-agent trap enable
 snmp-agent trap enable port-security
 undo snmp-agent sys-info version v3
 undo snmp-agent trap enable arp
 undo snmp-agent trap enable radius
 undo snmp-agent trap enable stp
column2:
#
 snmp-agent
 snmp-agent trap enable
 snmp-agent community write simple U-NET
 snmp-agent sys-info version v2c
 snmp-agent target-host trap address udp-domain 192.168.30.251 params securityname U-NET v2c
 undo snmp-agent trap enable ifmonitor
 undo snmp-agent trap enable mac-address
 snmp-agent trap enable port-security
 snmp-agent trap source Vlan-interface400
 undo snmp-agent sys-info version v3
 undo snmp-agent trap enable arp
 undo snmp-agent trap enable radius
 undo snmp-agent trap enable stp
 undo snmp-agent trap enable syslog
#
 ifmonitor crc-error slot 1 high-threshold 1000 low-threshold 100 interval 30
 ifmonitor input-error slot 1 high-threshold 1000 low-threshold 100 interval 30
 ifmonitor output-error slot 1 high-threshold 1000 low-threshold 100 interval 30
#
 undo gratuitous-arp-learning enable
 arp mac-interface-consistency check enable

column1:
#
local-user ura8su class manage
 password simple ura8suNW-SW!
 service-type telnet terminal
 authorization-attribute user-role network-admin
#
column2:

local-user ura8su class manage
